There are several things you can try to speed up your wiggly tooth falling out naturally on your own:
1. Gently wiggle it back and forth with your fingers for a few minutes each day;
2. Apply some table salt directly on the gum around the tooth - this creates a cleaning effect that can stimulate the tooth to come loose;
3. Have someone push it with their finger or very gently massage the gum with their fingers;
4. Try to swallow a small amount of salt water or juice to irritate the tooth and gums;
5. If you're feeling adventurous, you could try to pop it out with your teeth - some people say it works!;
For children, sugar-free hard candies or gum have been found to help in extracting baby teeth. The more you mess with it, the faster the extraction will happen.
